Al Lee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Al_Lee 0 Al Lee (born June 8, 1893) was a Boston-born American actor, producer and manager in vaudeville and silent films. Lee married actress Lilyan Tashman in 1914, but the couple divorced in 1921. Tashman met Lee while working on a double act with Eddie Cantor. Lee later went on to become a manager for George White's Scandals. Al_Lee ( born June_8_,_1893 ) was a_Boston-born_American_actor_,_producer_and_manager in vaudeville and silent_films .
